entry.title: New Kitchenaid
entry.content: This week, I purchased a new 6 quart Kitchenaid stand mixer from Costco! It was on sale for $320 from $400 and I couldn’t resist the temptation to upgrade my equipment and have a stand mixer that could make more rolls at a time!
